text: Am not a pizza lover but hubby is so pizza is part of our diet. Got a pizza supreme & I ate 3 piecesüòÅWent back a 2nd time and still great pizza so much toppings it was falling off great soft cheesy crust ... now a meal choice each week LOVE this place!

name: Angla Adorno
text: We stopped here for lunch on the way back from our trip. We had a group of 10 (4 adults, 6 teenagers 13-16). We waited about 30 mins, which for a group that size is OK. The pizza was very good I thought and the teenagers loved it. The staff that we had was great and very friendly. Can definitely recommend this place.

name: Shannon G.
text: $4 for delivery regardless of order size is insanity. Especially when the location is less than a 10 minute drive. I can get food 20 mins from me for .99 delivery fee. Not ordering from here until they lower this ridiculous fee.

name: Ashley White
text: We order from this Pizza Hut on a pretty regular basis. The wait time for our delivery has been pretty standard (roughly 30 minutes) with some delivery times being shorter and some longer. Our order has always been right and the food hot, ‚Ä¶More

name: Roseanne Bernard
text: Three of us came in on 12/6. We had no wait and we each ordered pizza with different toppings. We got extra cheese, mushrooms, peppers, onions and pepperoni. The pizzas were warm, extra cheesy and downright awesome. We will return!!

text: Bad experience again. Ordered an ultimate stuffed cheese. Came to pick up only to be told it's a seasonal item that's no longer available, even though they charged me for it. Was charged 22 bucks. Offered 10 buck credit for next time I order. No receipt or credit slip. Feel robbed and mediocre pizza. Don't use this place. Badly run.
